HEADWORD: Toothshell
<hw>Tooth"shell"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any species of <gen>Dentalium</gen> and allied genera having a
tooth-shaped shell. See <er>Dentalium</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

